SUMMARY:Triathlon Swim – Tuesday
DESCRIPTION:Outdoor pool\n\nDuration: 35–40 min\nYardage: 500–650 yd\nEff
 ort: RPE 3–4/10\n\nWarm-up\n4 x 50 easy\n\nTechnique\n4 x 25 catch-up dr
 ill\n4 x 25 fingertip drag\n\nMain set\n4 x 50 relaxed\n2 x 100 easy\n\n
 Cool-down\n50 easy\n\nCoach's cue\nBlow bubbles continuously underwater.
  Reach long before each pull.\n\nGoal\nFinish feeling like you could hav
 e done more.
LOCATION:Outdoor pool
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
