SUMMARY:Sprint Triathlon – Race Day Swim
DESCRIPTION:Race day: sprint triathlon swim.\n\nDistance: 750 m / about 8
 20 yd\n\nRace cues\nStart 10–15 seconds slower than you think.\nLong str
 okes.\nSteady bubbles underwater.\nLight flutter kick.\nSettle into rhyt
 hm before thinking about pace.\nExit the water relaxed for the bike.
LOCATION:Race venue
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
